{"tid":252054,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"放負 真係好唔開心","createTime":"2017-05-21T12:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T04:37:50.000Z","uid":22059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"140dd8fdceeae50b1609e03502664a930701abcf","tid":252054,"uid":22059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:21:15.000Z","msg":"以為多左個知心好友<br />\n<br />\n誰不知你同佢講既野 佢轉頭會同全世界講（我相信以佢把口出既版整本會再惡化意思）<br />\n<br />\n你有時候無心舉動 佢會幫你諗埋你既動機 但媽的 我根本咩都無諗過<br />\n<br />\n只可以講 我又成長左 知道原來最好咩都收埋自己 最好毒啞自己 最好咩人都唔再相信<br />\n<br />\n我只係希望自己唔好再去在意人地點睇自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999，大家可以唔覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔好屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7d359e18a7eeee67a5641f4169605c9b3dea6e","tid":252054,"uid":34801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a251cda725540bef385ef5d95bdd3c798c149e9f","tid":252054,"uid":22059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又是你"},{"pid":"62b16e30b53dc7d8eaa7c417c52dfba0509ff053","tid":252054,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"28656ddb352fd4b938ccde95f740a3809d3e88ff","tid":252054,"uid":22059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n我知我好小朋友 係真係想發洩 因為已經無信任既人了 對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：21歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58da411fadc1